<br>
I don't like using my mana to nuke.  If we get a over pull and need every heal I can pull out then I want that mana there to use for it.  <br>
<br>
I keep a few things up.  Root so if I or another caster is attacked I can hit a root and they can back away long enough for either a mez or the tanks to come rescue us. <br>
<br>
I don't want to be a sit and heal, sit and heal cleric if the area doesn't require it.  <br>
<br>
I don't want to be a sitting duck for the mobs unable to handle a few hits before the tanks get there. <br>
<br>
