As I spend most of my time with my Husband, a Shadowknight, and he makes an awesome tank, I am frequently the main healer for our group.  We have been in places where we were getting mad experience, and I rarely had to heal anyone at all.  I was free to melee and/or nuke, and still keep everyone healthy.<br>
