<br>
As far as the point someone made about the puller being shitty if the cleric has high mana... I have to disagree. Because I am good at managing my mana and still putting out damage doesn't make the pulling slow. When I play my cleric, Bajnok ( who is a 62 warrior with alot of HP and REALLY easy to heal ) is usually pulling, and he is consistently pulling multiples in places like Hate's Fury and such, which is the way we like to play. We find it exciting and challenging. Also, if you have a skilled group, the cleric usually won't have to heal anyone but the tank, because everyone is good at managing aggro and the tank is good at keeping aggro.<br>
<br>
